reviews.text: Was hungry and decided to Yelp some Asian food and this little gem pop up. It doesn't have the overall ratings you want to go too but didn't want to be...
Ordered the spicy beef noodle soup, didn't come with any beef. Looks good in the pictures tho
Came back here and got the beef with broccoli and my husband got the pho. It was all delicious and big portions!! The service was great too.
